    "created_at": "2014-07-01T15:58:01Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-07-01T15:58:01Z",
    "body": "Webpage has scripts, which access local files by providing relative path, for example `fs.readFileSync(Path.join(\"core\", \"config\", \"settings.json\"));` it does works only when I run\n\n`HIDE/bin: atom-shell/atom .`\nand breaks if I do\n`HIDE: atom-shell/atom bin`\n\nSeems like `_dirname` returns proper path. \n"
