    "created_at": "2014-07-01T16:31:52Z",
    "updated_at": "2014-07-01T16:31:52Z",
    "body": "That makes sense. You can definitely pass it in on every call, if you'd like. What I have done with my application is the following:\n\nin `main.js`:\n\n```\nglobal[\"__dirname\"] = __dirname\n```\n\nin `app.js`:\n\n```\nremote.getGlobal(\"__dirname\");\n```\n\nBut, whatever approach you take should have the desired result.\n"
  },
